  "prompt": "Where can I get all the episodes of the Doordarshan series \" Wagle Ki Duniya \"?",
  "response": "\"Wagle Ki Duniya\" is a classic Indian television series that aired on Doordarshan. If you're looking to watch all the episodes of the show, here are a few options:\n\n1. **YouTube**: Many episodes or clips from the series may be available on YouTube. You can search for the specific series and find uploads by various users.\n\n2. **Streaming Platforms**: Check popular streaming services such as Amazon Prime Video, Disney+ Hotstar, or others that might have classic Indian TV shows. Availability can vary by region.\n\n3. **DVDs or Digital Downloads**: Look for DVD collections or digital downloads on platforms like Flipkart or Amazon.\n\n4. **Social Media**: Sometimes, fan pages or groups on platforms like Facebook or Instagram may share episodes or links to where you can find them.\n\n5. **Doordarshan's Official Website or App**: As Doordarshan has started digitizing many of its classic shows, check their official website or any associated apps for availability.\n\nAlways ensure that you are accessing content through legal and authorized platforms to support the creators and copyright holders.",
